item.title: Easy wireframes with Moqups
item.description: Creating wireframes is a very tedious job, but now there is new webapp for that – unfortunately you don’t have to use iPhone to make really easy and quick wireframes. Only think which you need is only HTML5 browser, and a little bit of free time. Check it now: Moqups
